body:
### Doug Gabbard
Check out my page at www.dgabbard.com.   Some basic web page development using Word Press, nothing special.

```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

### Hobbies and Interests
Puzzles
Playing on computers - this web page for example
Running - lots of running.  5Ks, 10Ks, and more

### Authors and Contributors
You can @mention a GitHub username to generate a link to their profile. The resulting `<a>` element will link to the contributor's GitHub Profile. For example: In 2007, Chris Wanstrath (@defunkt), PJ Hyett (@pjhyett), and Tom Preston-Werner (@mojombo) founded GitHub.

### Built this with GitHub
Check out the documentation at https://help.github.com/pages
